# API URL for image upload
# Leave empty ("") when frontend is served by the Node.js server (recommended)
# Set to your server URL if frontend is hosted separately (e.g. Firebase Hosting)
# Examples:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://volt-construction.com
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-server.com:3001
#   VITE_API_URL=
VITE_API_URL=
